{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":60025,"duration_api_ms":59111,"num_turns":31,"result":"Done! I've completed the scout analysis for **Milestone 2: Context Compiler**. \n\n## Summary\n\nThe task adds task-scoped context assembly to prevent oversized prompts when working with large architecture documents. Here's what I found:\n\n**Key Integration Points:**\n- **lib/context.sh** (148 ‚Üí ~250 lines): Extend Milestone 1's token accounting with three new functions for keyword extraction, context packet building, and compression strategies\n- **stages/coder.sh** (line 210‚Äì219): Replace raw block concatenation with `build_context_packet()` when `CONTEXT_COMPILER_ENABLED=true`; architecture stays full for coder\n- **stages/review.sh** (line 34‚Äì47): Filter architecture blocks to sections referencing files modified by coder\n- **stages/tester.sh** (line 24‚Äì33): Filter context to relevant test-scoped sections\n- **lib/config.sh** (line 109): Add single `CONTEXT_COMPILER_ENABLED=false` default\n- **templates/pipeline.conf.example** (line 210): Document the new config key\n\n**Critical Implementation Details:**\n1. Keyword extraction from task string + `CODER_SUMMARY.md` \"Files Modified\" section\n2. Simple awk-based markdown section filtering by `##` headings\n3. Compression priority order: prior tester context ‚Üí non-blocking notes ‚Üí prior progress (never compress architecture/task)\n4. Fallback to full injection if keyword matching yields zero results\n5. Prompt note injected when compression occurs: `[Context compressed: <component> reduced from N to M lines]`\n\nThe SCOUT_REPORT.md is now ready in your project root.","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"f07d4a30-a3bc-4910-bb2a-910e21ab7552","total_cost_usd":0.17400200000000002,"usage":{"input_tokens":98,"cache_creation_input_tokens":58126,"cache_read_input_tokens":708565,"output_tokens":6078,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":58126,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-haiku-4-5":{"inputTokens":98,"outputTokens":6078,"cacheReadInputTokens":708565,"cacheCreationInputTokens":58126,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.17400200000000002,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"0c4de771-2733-4cb2-886d-46e215acf72f"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":322432,"duration_api_ms":307074,"num_turns":41,"result":"Milestone 2: Context Compiler is complete. Here's the summary:\n\n**6 files modified, 1 file created:**\n- `lib/context.sh` ‚Äî Added 6 new functions (~200 lines) for keyword extraction, section filtering, compression, and the main `build_context_packet()` entry point\n- `lib/config.sh` ‚Äî Added `CONTEXT_COMPILER_ENABLED=false` default\n- `stages/coder.sh`, `stages/review.sh`, `stages/tester.sh` ‚Äî Integrated `build_context_packet()` calls before context budget reporting\n- `templates/pipeline.conf.example` ‚Äî Documented the new config key\n- `tests/test_context_compiler.sh` ‚Äî 31 new tests\n\n**All 41 tests pass. Shellcheck clean on all modified files. Feature is off by default (`CONTEXT_COMPILER_ENABLED=false`), preserving 1.0 behavior.**","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"933c03f8-2e17-464a-b6dd-21f4aa6c34c6","total_cost_usd":2.2173445000000003,"usage":{"input_tokens":36,"cache_creation_input_tokens":88138,"cache_read_input_tokens":2491304,"output_tokens":16826,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":88138,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-opus-4-6":{"inputTokens":36,"outputTokens":16826,"cacheReadInputTokens":2491304,"cacheCreationInputTokens":88138,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":2.2173445000000003,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"d733b86f-729e-45cf-b81f-ca01796b6139"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":248203,"duration_api_ms":247431,"num_turns":15,"result":"**Verdict: CHANGES_REQUIRED**\n\nOne complex blocker was found and confirmed via live execution:\n\n**Preamble fallback bug** (`lib/context.sh`): When `extract_relevant_sections` is called with keywords that match no `##` sections, it returns the document's preamble (the text before the first `##` heading ‚Äî always present in files like ARCHITECTURE.md). `_filter_block` then sees this shorter, non-empty, non-identical string and applies it, replacing the full document with just the preamble. This silently strips all architecture section content from agent context whenever no keywords match any section heading/body.\n\nThe spec requires \"when keywords yield zero matches, full artifact is used (fallback to 1.0)\" ‚Äî this guarantee is violated. The fix is to either have `extract_relevant_sections` return empty when no `##` sections are included in the result, or have `_filter_block` require at least one `##` heading in the filtered output before applying it.","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"19061fbd-8a9e-4e66-b635-5957a10dcb2b","total_cost_usd":0.6462494999999999,"usage":{"input_tokens":11,"cache_creation_input_tokens":82048,"cache_read_input_tokens":513005,"output_tokens":12309,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":82048,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-sonnet-4-6":{"inputTokens":11,"outputTokens":12309,"cacheReadInputTokens":513005,"cacheCreationInputTokens":82048,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.6462494999999999,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"fe1d103b-2d16-4769-b191-c0f27522b50d"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":167869,"duration_api_ms":152464,"num_turns":19,"result":"Rework complete. Here's what I fixed:\n\n**Complex Blocker: Preamble fallback bug in `_filter_block`** (`lib/context.sh`):\n- When a document had preamble text before the first `##` heading and no sections matched keywords, `extract_relevant_sections` returned only the preamble. `_filter_block` then applied this shorter result, silently stripping all architecture content.\n- **Fix**: Added a heading-presence check ‚Äî if the original had `##` headings but the filtered result has none, fall back to the original. This preserves the spec guarantee that zero keyword matches use the full artifact.\n- **Test added**: New test case covering the exact scenario (preamble + sections + non-matching keywords).\n\nAll 41 tests pass, `bash -n` passes on the modified file.","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"8cd469cf-9027-48bf-b982-d6aa1268924e","total_cost_usd":0.6297004999999999,"usage":{"input_tokens":18,"cache_creation_input_tokens":34896,"cache_read_input_tokens":598071,"output_tokens":4499,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":34896,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-opus-4-6":{"inputTokens":18,"outputTokens":4499,"cacheReadInputTokens":598071,"cacheCreationInputTokens":34896,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.6297004999999999,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"84c06b87-fac9-469c-9ade-a506bcf72d5c"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":99415,"duration_api_ms":99293,"num_turns":7,"result":"**Verdict: APPROVED_WITH_NOTES**\n\nThe complex blocker from cycle 1 is verified fixed. The heading-presence check in `_filter_block` (lines 405‚Äì410) correctly detects preamble-only filtered results and falls back to the full original, satisfying the spec guarantee \"zero matches ‚Üí full artifact.\" The new test at line 325 directly covers the bug scenario.\n\nNo regressions introduced by the rework. The four pre-existing non-blocking notes from cycle 1 (gawk `IGNORECASE`, redundant export, missing `local j`, mixed `[ ]`/`[[ ]]`) are still present and carry forward. One coverage gap remains (direct `_compress_if_over_budget` test).","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"8c8dc2e2-bc9e-4a82-aa74-efd16d92cbe8","total_cost_usd":0.302265,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":49664,"cache_read_input_tokens":141740,"output_tokens":4899,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":49664,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-sonnet-4-6":{"inputTokens":6,"outputTokens":4899,"cacheReadInputTokens":141740,"cacheCreationInputTokens":49664,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.302265,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"65b016c2-870c-49d0-8116-0f2e79627aee"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":213175,"duration_api_ms":198370,"num_turns":13,"result":"Done. Added 8 tests for `_compress_if_over_budget` to `tests/test_context_compiler.sh`:\n\n1. **Under budget ‚Äî no-op**: Verifies no compression when context is within budget\n2. **Over budget ‚Äî PRIOR_TESTER_CONTEXT compressed first**: Verifies it's the first priority\n3. **Note injection**: Verifies `[Context compressed: PRIOR_TESTER_CONTEXT reduced from N to M lines]` format\n4. **First priority suffices ‚Äî NON_BLOCKING_CONTEXT untouched**: Verifies compression stops when budget is met\n5. **Priority: skip empty PRIOR_TESTER_CONTEXT ‚Üí NON_BLOCKING_CONTEXT**: Verifies second-priority fallthrough\n6. **PRIOR_TESTER_CONTEXT stays empty**: Verifies the skip-empty logic doesn't corrupt empty vars\n7. **Priority: skip both first two ‚Üí PRIOR_PROGRESS_CONTEXT**: Verifies third-priority fallthrough\n\nTotal: 40 tests in the file, 41 total across the suite ‚Äî all passing.","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"d9b0dc9f-d034-4b4f-9df6-2f5a0aa1a6ec","total_cost_usd":0.5402566499999999,"usage":{"input_tokens":12,"cache_creation_input_tokens":54043,"cache_read_input_tokens":524498,"output_tokens":12014,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":54043,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-sonnet-4-6":{"inputTokens":12,"outputTokens":12014,"cacheReadInputTokens":524498,"cacheCreationInputTokens":54043,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.5402566499999999,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"bddf7dd1-2e0d-414e-a29e-ad54f5e6a5b1"}

